message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and question answering. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of deep learning models, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it involves training and evaluating models, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as it deals with finding relevant information from a given text, and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks.
